<p align="center">北斗三号卫星团队在发射场合影。</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200801/1d1cc8c674a24947a715b75c73d6b93f.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
